! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|0.2.18 |2026-04-07 |Cleanup: replace \define with \procedure/\function, extract inline SVGs to icon tiddlers, move demo-nav styles to stylesheet, replace hardcoded colors with palette variables |
|v0.2.17 |2026-04-03 |Include AdvancedPerformance info-bar in app layout (safe no-op if plugin not installed) |
|v0.2.16 |2026-04-02 |FAB sets all `rimir/appify/*` help contexts dynamically instead of just top-level `rimir/appify` |
|v0.2.15 |2026-03-30 |Add `defaultContext` attribute to LLM chat panel (`rimir/appify rimir/typed tw-gotchas shortcuts`) |
|v0.2.14 |2026-03-30 |Add JS-based edge/corner resize to LLM chat panel. Per-topic llm-help context paths |
|v0.2.13 |2026-03-30 |Per-chat help context — FAB sets `rimir/appify` on the appify chat tiddler's `llm-help-context` field instead of the global tiddler. Remove global context cleanup from delete-app and wiki-mode switch |
|v0.2.12 |2026-03-30 |Fix dropdown checkboxes in app chat — skip `fabWidget.refresh()` when fab is hidden (app mode), preventing duplicate widget trees with conflicting `$click-outside` handlers |
|v0.2.11 |2026-03-29 |Use shared chat toolbar from llm-connect — pin, export/import, tool selector, context selector now inherited from `chat-toolbar.tid` instead of duplicated |
|v0.2.10 |2026-03-29 |Rename llm-help context key from `appify` to `rimir/appify` — consistent namespacing across all plugins |
|v0.2.9 |2026-03-28 |Auto-set `appify` help context — FAB adds/removes `appify` from `$:/temp/rimir/llm-help/active-context` on app activate/deactivate; delete-app also cleans up context |
|v0.2.8 |2026-03-25 |Switch LLM chat panel protection from whitelist to blacklist (deny mode, base filter: tag[sensitive]); remove condition indicator from stacked edit tabs; remove dead CSS |
|v0.2.7 |2026-03-28 |Migrate LLM docs from custom llm-doc/context_guide system to llm-help pages (context-scoped, discoverable via llm_help tool). Remove old llm-doc tiddlers and context_guide tool. Update chat panel prompt to use llm_help |
|v0.2.6 |2026-03-23 |Fix app-to-app switching via FAB (refresh now detects tiddler attribute changes); update README.md |
|v0.2.5 |2026-03-21 |Fix stacked view tab switching with effective-tab fallback; fix block-level wikitext parsing in transcluded views ($mode=block); remove debug output; refactor esc() to module level |
|v0.2.4 |2026-03-21 |Conditional split pane visibility (condition filters on nodes); stacked views / tab groups; enhanced edit mode (maximal layout, tabbed stacked editor, inline condition editing, view dropdown with tag-based lookup, per-view clone button, per-view edit overlay); view selector and condition editor extracted to wikitext templates |
|v0.2.3 |2026-03-19 |LLM integration (chat panel, context_guide tool, progressive disclosure docs); clone/delete app actions; live refresh for proportions and splits changes |
|v0.2.2 |2026-03-18 |Extract edit overlay to wikitext tiddler; hide title editor and TW controls in edit overlay |
|v0.2.1 |2026-03-18 |In-app tiddler editor (full EditTemplate with draft lifecycle); grid-area-aware drag handles; CSS cleanup |
|v0.2.0 |2026-03-18 |Edit mode modals: channel editor, rule editor, debug inspector; layout switching with config persistence; focus layout |
|v0.1.0 |2026-03-17 |Initial release: app renderer, FAB launcher, 4 layout templates, demo app |
